{"tid":2111632,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE仔又贏 灣仔總部又中","createTime":"2020-07-16T16:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T06:15:29.000Z","uid":139689,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8699b9b8505ac4113ca3b959af6fcbb09335dba3","tid":2111632,"uid":139689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"Dear Colleagues,<br />\n<br />\nEarly this morning (16/7), we were informed by a student of the BABA programme that she has contracted with COVID-19. The class attended by the student was held in Room 802 from 7:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m. on 14 Jul 2020.  Once we became aware of the situation, the use of Room 802 and female toilet on 8/F and 9/F was immediately suspended and EHSD was contacted to arrange deep cleaning and disinfection work in the affected area.  <br />\n<br />\nAll PEAK staff should stay vigilant during this period.  If you have a fever or flu-like symptoms, please seek medical assistance immediately, report to your Team Leader, and refrain from work.  Please continue to be vigilant and maintain good personal and environmental hygiene.<br />\n<br />\nShould you have any enquiries, please contact PEAK Administration Office.<br />\n<br />\nStay healthy and safe.<br />\n<br />\nBest regards"},{"pid":"578043e66ee6ff0a0c9c3eb1aa1db35385682ed2","tid":2111632,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"Diu ah"},{"pid":"132530a2cf70ab4938a660cb93607bef5a0e360a","tid":2111632,"uid":78336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"收手啦，無人想理你ive仔阿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a272248e49ce944f45b8bf82548b319f19a8ad9","tid":2111632,"uid":247173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"132530a2cf70ab4938a660cb93607bef5a0e360a","tid":2111632,"uid":78336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"收手啦，無人想理你ive仔阿 <i